      ],
      "source": "https://sweetwaterriverdeck.com/our-story/"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "In 2016 the Iles family purchased the site and reopened it as Sweetwater Marina & Riverdeck, adding a new restaurant and event space.",
